(40211, 'Luo Xiao Hei Zhan Ji (Movie)', 'A prequel film to the Luo Xiao Hei Zhan Ji web anime. Viewers will discover how Xiao Hei obtained the last name Luo. It is also expected episode 28 of the web series will be released right before the feature film airs in theaters after a 2 year hiatus.', '2019-09-07', '0000-00-00', 10, 'https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1957/102430.jpg', 'https://myanimelist.net/anime/40211/Luo_Xiao_Hei_Zhan_Ji_Movie'),
